article:
'Listing' may refer to:
* Enumeration of a set of items in the form of a list
* Johann Benedict Listing, mathematician
* Listing (computer), a computer code listing
* Listing (finance), the placing of a company's shares on the list of stocks
  traded on a stock exchange
* Listing (tilting) of vessels in a nautical context
* Designation as a listed building in the United Kingdom
* A term in US real estate brokerage, referring to the obtaining of a written
  contract to represent the seller of a property or business
